Resolution order inside `getInstanceFromField()`:
1. `\App\Modules\{Module}\UiTypes\{Suffix}` — module-specific override
2. `\App\Modules\Base\UiTypes\{Suffix}` — base implementation
3. `BaseUiType` — generic fallback (renders `String.tpl`)

